	(text "Bits from ADC\n0-Up Pin 1 Up/Z - LSB - was hard-wired to both reads pin 1\n1-Dn Pin 2 Dn/Y - was hard-wired to both reads pin 2\n2-Lf Pin 3 Lf/X\n3-Rt Pin 4 Right/Mode\n4-X Pin 3 Left/X Mux 2(1A) First Read Pin 3\n5-Y Pin 2 Down/Y\n6-Z Pin 1 Up/Z\n7-Mode Pin 4 Right/Mode\n\nPort Pin 7 Select goes thru inverter NPN to ADC3"
